span></span></span>
其中，p表示程序可并发的部分占整个程序的比例。</p>

<h2 id="第二讲并行架构">第二讲：并行架构</h2>

<h2 id="并行架构">并行架构</h2>

<h3 id="flynns-taxonomy分类法">Flynn’s Taxonomy（分类法）</h3>

<h4 id="定义一种并行架构的分类方法">定义：一种并行架构的分类方法</h4>

<p>A classification of computer architectures based on the number of streams of instructions and data</p>

<p><img src="assets/1561360604887.png" alt="1561360604887" /></p>

<h5 id="sisd-architecture">SISD Architecture</h5>

<p><img src="assets/1561360717822.png" alt="1561360717822" /></p>

<p>例如：单核计算机</p>

<h5 id="simd-architecture单指令多数据流">SIMD Architecture:单指令多数据流</h5>

<p><img src="assets/1561360792439.png" alt="1561360792439" /></p>

<p>例子：vector processor,GPUs</p>

<p><img src="assets/1561360831768.png" alt="1561360831768" /></p>

<p>延申：SPMD,对称多处理器</p>

